    <item>
      <title>电子巨头富士康进军电动汽车领域，实现业务多元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/electronics-giant-foxconn-looks-to-diversify-with-ev-foray</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾工业巨头富士康正在台北举办年度科技日。该公司正式名称为鸿海，是全球最大的电子产品代工制造商。现在，该公司面临着多元化发展和建立更具未来保障的收入来源的需求。我们的科技记者 Annabelle Droulers 展望了未来的机遇和挑战。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/electronics-giant-foxconn-looks-to-diversify-with-ev-foray</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行称超长期债券收益率差距接近二十年来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/japan-s-super-long-yield-gap-near-biggest-in-two-decades-on-boj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者预期日本央行将推迟进一步加息，日本最长期限政府债券收益率相对于较短期债券的收益率已攀升至近二十年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/japan-s-super-long-yield-gap-near-biggest-in-two-decades-on-boj</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:50:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新评估刺激政策押注，中国股市涨势减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-stocks-surge-on-return-from-holidays-as-euphoria-extends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一周假期过后，中国境内股市一度上涨，但随后迅速回落，原因是交易员对北京出台更多刺激措施的决心产生了质疑。香港股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-stocks-surge-on-return-from-holidays-as-euphoria-extends</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>假期过后，中国主权债券延续刺激措施引发的下跌趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-sovereign-bonds-extend-stimulus-led-slump-after-holidays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在刺激措施引发的股市狂热中，避险资产需求减弱，导致中国政府债券价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-sovereign-bonds-extend-stimulus-led-slump-after-holidays</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:14:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
