      <title>Pictet 文件错误地显示了 150 亿美元的中国银行押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/pictet-filing-mistakenly-showed-15-billion-bet-on-chinese-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据这家瑞士资产管理公司称，一份香港交易所文件错误地显示，百达资产管理公司向中国建设银行股份有限公司投资了 1212 亿港元（156 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/pictet-filing-mistakenly-showed-15-billion-bet-on-chinese-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 00:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国恢复经济后油价下跌，交易员关注中东局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员关注中东的敌对行动，以及中国结束一周假期后出台进一步刺激措施的前景，油价在连续五天上涨之后出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 23:27:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市开盘飙升，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市上涨，赶上了受刺激措施推动的股市涨势，这些措施是在一周假期后重新开市。亚洲股市普遍下跌，日元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 22:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
